<BaseLayout title="Markdown Syntax Cheat Sheet: A Complete Reference | ToolCalcs" description="A comprehensive Markdown reference covering headings, emphasis, lists, links, images, code blocks, tables, blockquotes, and GitHub Flavored Markdown extensions with practical examples for every syntax element." structuredData={structuredData}>
